        <div>
            <p class="text-lg">GWS Tool Group is committed to providing customer, employee, and stakeholder value and satisfaction while ensuring our workers’ safety and the protection of the environment where we work and live. <br><br> GWS Tool Group is committed to achieving this by:</p>
