         <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-8">
            <h3 class="text-white text-2xl font-black uppercase">Environmental Health and Safety Policy</h3>
            <p class="mb-4 text-lg">This policy applies to all operational Environment, Health and Safety (EHS) activities at Sandvik controlled locations. It applies to all entities within the Sandvik Group and covers all employees, contracted workers and visitors to Sandvik facilities. The full version of the EHS policy is available in Sandvik’s corporate governance framework, The Sandvik Way.</p>
            <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Environment</h4>
                <p>Sandvik commits to protecting the environment. To achieve this, we will reduce our greenhouse gas emissions to reach our net zero target, prevent pollution, protect biodiversity, reduce water withdrawal, enhance circularity and use energy, input materials and other resources efficiently.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Health and Safety</h4>
                <p>Sandvik commits to providing healthy and safe workplaces. We will continue to reduce mental and physical injuries and illness, and involve our employees in health and well-being activities.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Legal Compliance</h4>
                <p>Sandvik will maintain a systematic approach to comply with or exceed applicable EHS legal and other requirements.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Continual Improvement</h4>
